  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec ┬з6 Vertical-Slice Validation Target">Full walkthrough must complete with 11 pillar acceptance checks: persona, tools, workspace state in prompt, memory composition, `/summarize` triggers `invoke_playbook`, routes via engine, output renders schema-aware, Context pane trace, Send to Workspace + Make it shorter + `/clear`, conversational refinement.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec Phase D exit criterion 5">All R6 changes have integration test coverage тАФ vertical-slice is the binding artifact.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-02">BFF publish-size тЙд+5 MB total across R6; per-task verification required for BFF-touching tasks. This test may add BFF test fixtures тАФ measure publish-size delta.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-01">Conversational refinement after playbook output must work; agent stays conversational.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">Existing PublicContracts facades used; no new facade for testing.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Trace event capture must show: tool name + decision + timestamp only; no user message text.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Verify publish-size compressed; report delta in task notes.</constraint>
  </constraints>

