        Arrange: seed sprk_aipersona row + sprk_analysistool rows + sprk_analysisaction with outputSchema + sprk_analysisplaybook with node FK. Act: invoke `/summarize #file.docx` via BFF chat endpoint. Assert: per-pillar checks (11 acceptance criteria from spec ┬з6).
