  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">
      Check context. Output: "ЁЯФТ RIGOR LEVEL: STANDARD тАФ Vertical-slice integration test; validation-only; high-stakes coverage breadth". Read project CLAUDE.md + spec ┬з6.
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress + Dependency Verification">
      Read TASK-INDEX.md; confirm 087 status is ЁЯФ▓, deps 029/049/079/084/085/086 ALL тЬЕ. Verify ALL prior Phase A/B/C/D component tasks completed before starting. Update `current-task.md`.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">
      Read spec ┬з6 Vertical-Slice Validation Target verbatim (11 acceptance bullets). Read AI-ARCHITECTURE.md + chat-architecture.md + playbook-architecture.md for end-to-end flow. Identify the BFF integration-test project + the frontend e2e test framework.
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Build BFF Integration Test">
      Create `tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/VerticalSlice/SummarizeVerticalSliceTests.cs`. Seed Dataverse rows (persona + tools + action + playbook FK). Invoke BFF chat endpoint with `/summarize #file.docx` payload. Capture telemetry + assert per-pillar checks (1-7, 9): persona, tools, invoke_playbook, engine FK, output schema, workspace state in prompt, memory composition, widget visibility filter.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Build Frontend e2e Test">
      Create `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/tests/e2e/summarize-vertical-slice.e2e.test.ts`. Drive UI via Playwright or ui-test skill. Verify: (a) `/summarize #file.docx` parses correctly (Pillar 8); (b) workspace tab created with bulleted tldr + labeled entities (Pillar 5); (c) Context pane shows execution trace (Pillar 6c); (d) "Send to Workspace" button works (Pillar 6b); (e) "Make it shorter" refinement gets conversational response (NFR-01); (f) `/clear` resets session without LLM call (Pillar 8 hard slash).
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Run Full Suite + Verify 11 Pillar Checks">
      Run BFF test: `dotnet test --filter "FullyQualifiedName~SummarizeVerticalSlice"`. Run frontend e2e: `npm run test:e2e`. Walk through each of the 11 spec ┬з6 acceptance bullets; mark each green. Capture trace event log + verify ADR-015 hygiene (no user message text).
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="BFF Publish-Size Verification (NFR-02)">
      Run `dotnet publish -c Release src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ -o deploy/api-publish/`. Measure compressed size. Report delta vs prior baseline (Phase C exit task 079). Confirm cumulative R6 delta тЙд +5 MB per NFR-02. Hard ceiling 60 MB per ADR-029.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
      Walk through every &lt;acceptance-criterion&gt; below. Confirm each is testable + green.
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Document + Complete">
      Update task POML status. Update TASK-INDEX.md: 087 ЁЯФ▓ тЖТ тЬЕ. Reset `current-task.md`. Record BFF publish-size delta in task notes. Report completion + downstream unblock (088).
    </step>
  </steps>

